      <abstract id="aspace_5cd64f5cf65a446743d94ab60abd4239">The Patricia Turner Ritchie Collection
        on Brocks Gap, 1750s-1990s, is comprised exclusively of photocopies of deeds, wills,
        surveys, patents, road agreements, accounts, letters and a wide variety of other documents
        relevant to the Brocks Gap area of northwestern Rockingham County, Virginia.</abstract>
    </did>
    <descgrp type="admininfo">
      <head>Administrative Information</head>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_2f9229ee48362d234c3d94935a3755b0">
